comment: Bogut (GSW) makes incidental contact with Horford (ATL) as he attempts to knock away the pass.
LHH shows that Horford (ATL) changes his pivot foot after securing the pass.
Millsap (ATL) does not intentionally kick the ball on the play.
RATR shows that Thompson (GSW) and Green (GSW) make incidental contact with Schroder (ATL) that does not affect his movement to the basket or layup attempt.
Bogut (GSW) sets the screen on Sefolosha (ATL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Korver (ATL) and Green (GSW) briefly engage and separate away from the ball.
Barnes (GSW) makes contact with Millsap's (ATL) arm and body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Thompson's (GSW) driving layup attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Thompson.
Horford (ATL) sets the screen on Livingston (GSW) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Thompson (GSW) does not extend his arm into Millsap (ATL) as he creates space for the jump shot attempt.
Livingston (GSW) makes incidental contact with Schroder (ATL) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Bazemore (ATL) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Correctly called OOB last touched by Millsap (ATL). Golden State retained possession.

Horford (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on the drive to the basket and shot attempt by Thompson (GSW). Thompson slips and falls on the drive to the basket, and not as a result of any contact initiated by Horford.

Bogut (GSW) maintains legal guarding position with Bazemore (ATL) on the shot attempt, beating Bazemore to the spot and firming up his position when Bazemore initiates contact. He does not deliver contact.
Green (GSW) splits his feet on the perimeter at the start of his drive.
LATR shows that Millsap (ATL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Green (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Thompson (GSW) makes contact with Bazemore's (ATL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (ATL) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Green (GSW) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Bogut (GSW) dislodges Millsap (ATL) affecting his ability to retrieve the rebound.
Bogut (GSW) makes incidental contact with Schroder (ATL) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Schroder's (ATL) arms that affects his driving shot attempt.
Livingston (GSW) makes contact with Millsap's (ATL) body and head during his layup attempt.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Green (GSW) was behind the three point line on his shot attempt was confirmed.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Schroder's (ATL) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bazemore (ATL) commits a take foul on Thompson (GSW).
